Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.49,0:00:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為父親工作的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親和妹妹要去國外生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的獨居生活就從今年春天開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我第一次的獨居生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.20,0:00:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅持續數日之後 便迎來了終結
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 六花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也該起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就要去上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一年前封印中二病的黑歷史後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.54,0:00:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備開始全新高中生活的那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這位小鳥游六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來吧 小鳥游六花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 邪王真眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒的時刻到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:07.48,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}I WANT ONLY ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:24.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}廊下 夢が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:30.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}約束しても　心がどこかで怯えてるみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:33.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一人じゃないって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:35.85,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}信じたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:41.56,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思い続けてる だけで幸せなんて言えないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:47.36,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}虚ろな自信背負っていても　君が笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:53.49,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}そして私の勇気になる 一つの言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.09,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君の世界を変えられたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:00.62,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}二つの恋が進化する
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:04.84,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}本当だよ　巡らせた迷いが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.19,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}見つけた答えは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:10.07,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつでも君に導かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}届ける覚悟が 様にならなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.36,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}素直に伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.01,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}心のあるまま 声がきらめく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:21.29,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}WE COME VOIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:25.80,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}響き渡るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:24.15,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}走廊 夢想延續
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:30.00,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}儘管許下約定 心中某處依舊膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:33.10,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:35.85,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}明明想要這樣相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:41.56,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}思念不斷滋生 但是卻無法說出幸福二字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:47.36,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}雖背負著虛無的自信 你依然嘴角上揚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:53.49,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的一句話就能成為我的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.09,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}若能改變你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:00.62,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就能進化成為兩份愛戀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:04.84,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}真的哦 冥思苦想依舊迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.19,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}最終找到的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:10.07,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}無論何時都能引領著你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.60,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}就算沒有做好能夠傳達給你的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.36,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}大聲地說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.01,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}心靈深處的聲音熠熠生輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:25.80,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}響亮地傳達給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花 早餐吃煎蛋怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把裏面炸焦一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(395,438)\fs21}Darkside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.67,0:02:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,438)\fs21}up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就炸單面雞蛋囉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,438)\fs21}Sunnyside up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回合結束
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}請做雙面的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不該和你討論那些事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校服上的絲帶不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是他們幹的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要你昨天準備好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要開門嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼忙的時候你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拔掉你的呆毛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 那可是我的萌點所在！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.79,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(486,438)\fs21}Charm Point
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今年春天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花母親也因為工作而離開了這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花也和我一樣也開始了獨居生活 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼六花的行李被搬出來了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙終於也開始行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 爺爺搞錯了不小心退約了屋子？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然採用那種妨礙行為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到新的屋子前只能放在這裏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急代碼444發動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 六花就暫時住在這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.67,0:03:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太來叫我的話 起床後好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒也替我想想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.40,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)\pos(250,10)\3c&H000000&}Episode 1 復活的…邪王真眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓「聖調理人」叫我的話是不會這麼舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(261,438)\fs21}Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應付十花的借口是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「已經找到了間單身公寓 讓六花住過去了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣矇混了差不多一周
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱美拉 我把惡魔的果實賜予你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該對紅色的果實有抗性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有任何根據
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也稍微吃一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃起來像草莓一樣很美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會是那樣呢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太你越來越像「聖調理人」了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(512,438)\fs21}Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是被影響了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是為了你才這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,液體！綠色的毒液襲擊了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等等等 待著別動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便擦掉的話會擴散的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣在上面輕壓…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且…我們也算在交往中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是在交往中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後應該怎樣繼續讓戀愛升溫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於沒有和普通的女孩子交往過的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個患有中二病的女朋友難度實在是高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果順其自然的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就會和這之前沒什麼改變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(408,438)\fs21}Guten Morgen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫丹生谷森夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就上高中二年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.72,0:05:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 各位同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也請多多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.06,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高二出道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天約好的事情一定要遵守哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用聖書體書寫而來自魔術協會的劍魔結界攻擊是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:35.92,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}註：聖書體：古埃及象形文字系統中最正式的一種書寫體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.97,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就是從那由他的平行世界來訪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:39.55,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}註：那由他：梵語音譯，意為「多到沒有數目可以計算」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個也錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要使用凱米拉來進行薛定諤的貓實驗…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會做啦 可不要那麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你現在住在我家這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 是這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然只有這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天再去房屋中介看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的據點的話 我已經找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.32,0:06:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是普通人無法察覺的邪王的魔界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄得我認真起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔掉你呆毛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大清早就那麼親熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一色啦 一色誠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啦 下屬於輕音樂部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切奉獻給茴香學姐的男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來是小平頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥布林先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫我小平頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的我已經不存在了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 這個搖滾髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.77,0:06:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的頭髮是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來一趟生活指導辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平頭以後好像髮質就變了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐 早晨好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰來著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花 富堅同學 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始你們也就是二年級了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茴香學姐終於也變成三年級學生了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人沮喪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟也要參加升學考試啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是因為這個但還是很沮喪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三年級學生是殘念級學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.06,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}注：此为冷笑话，日语中的三年（さんねん）和残念（ざんねん）仅差一个音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣說就沒問題 書上明明是這麼寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…學姐 那個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得看著小森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想著要去逗大家開心 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升年級 什麼事都會發生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼了 穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安 茴香學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照校規這才是正常著裝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴安？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是高級裝傻？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐稍微過來一下 我有話要說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小森大人 你要拉我去哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在新的一年裏我們也朝氣蓬勃地開始學習生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:03.19,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都給我看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然以前一直接二連三地失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是升入二年級以後 我一定會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要勇攀高峰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:12.58,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面有請新生代表發言 凸守早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.04,0:08:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌駕於這座學校的頂點之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是新生代表 凸守早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.11,0:08:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這春風送暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.69,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬物復甦的美好時節
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:29.22,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的學習生活就要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她比去年丹生谷同學學習成績還要好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家也都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界是分為白色世界和黑色世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要看見精靈的話 正直的心靈是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:08:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 丹生谷同學因為貧血暈倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙到底在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又被分到同一個班了呢 光明之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢 小鳥游同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥游同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是同班哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也多多關照哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任也還是七瀨老師哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們讓我在明天之前要把頭髮剪掉 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道 這是你自己的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 你也還是和我們一個班？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我在隔壁的三班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才鬆了一口氣吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在全球都在變暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.54,0:09:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}註：日語中"鬆口氣"和"變暖"諧音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富堅同學 能麻煩出來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位美女是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 你是富堅同學的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.77,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還真是半斤八兩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們又分到一個班了所以先告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經跟小鳥游約定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我初中的事情絕對要守口如瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然又做了這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.72,0:09:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在春假的時候考慮過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是為了什麼才來這所高中的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能要在那麼冷門的社團裏待上三年…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼的隨從 雷霆戰錘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(434,438)\fs21}Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(532,438)\fs21}Mjolnir Hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守早苗 在此轉世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我凸守在替身形態出現時實施攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是冒牌森大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然本性邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊向左轉 左邊向右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在相反的旋轉下次元和空間就會產生扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現有基礎上再次加以旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.19,0:10:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會產生無窮的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 雷霆一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘔…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平衡感很差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守是不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是有活力的新生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:49.04,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濃厚奶酪 6個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為獎勵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你最喜歡的奶酪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給~你~吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有點過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放過任何一點苗頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在播放通知
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級四班的小鳥游同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥游六花同學請立刻到辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年級四班的小鳥游同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請馬上來辦公室一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校被恐怖分子佔領了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的 不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 從學校大概寄出了三封
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是全部被退回了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因為在這個世界上我存在的痕跡已經被抹去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然電話好像也是空號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已不存在於世上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你現在在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在總是可以聯繫上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛 眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.75,0:11:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這借口也太爛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣算是矇混過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是長此以往也不是辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.66,0:12:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情地吃一頓 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花也來這邊坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是夢魔沉睡的靈柩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是經過黑暗磨練的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近那裏也是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在那裏睡覺的時候做過很可怕的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 什麼樣的夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光 光明之物妄想對這個身體……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是疑問句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你 住的地方你想住哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續剛才說的話題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於新的據點和佈陣的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據點的話 邪王真眼和闇炎之主神臨之地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.32,0:12:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.40,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好也是魔導磁場最強的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.64,0:12:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種地方當然是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿成這樣是在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然趁我不在的時候居然把我的話劇部服裝弄成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裏面睡覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺？那還真是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去尋找新的據點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先少說兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據點？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給你找個合適的獨居的地方還真是不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想找一個地下迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者中世紀的城堡也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.18,0:13:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會有那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店的對面有一座寫著愛琴海的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 那個絕對不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到那裏房租那麼貴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我也覺得那裏房租應該會很貴 所以只是說說而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其實我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 肯定很貴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到新的據點之後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不能回這裏來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管是上學還是放學都不會經過這裏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的確是有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算魔界有騷動 也不能去勇太的屋子裏報告了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個的話 你不用來也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.13,0:14:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上去上學的時候我會去找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也會找你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量找個近點的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想一直跟我在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹生谷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥游的家完全空了啊 怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小六花搬家了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來解釋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十花…小姐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我去意大利的日子越來越近了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻遲遲不告訴我你的新家地址
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話也不接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 看來這是死活都不肯說的情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然尾隨著冒牌森大人過來是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就由我隨從凸守來為你們爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,438)\fs21}Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人你們快逃到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道對手是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在過去的對戰中讓凸守吃了臭奶酪的「聖調理人」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(661,438)\fs21}Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為對手正好不過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你的手 手！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:15:59.89,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你們的想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…這位冒牌森大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說些什麼呢 這是你有錯在先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守是很尊敬「聖調理人」的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(497,438)\fs21}Priestess
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為主人的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(499,438)\fs21}Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意以下屬的身份跟隨她到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然就神情慌張混淆視聽倒戈敵方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位關係還是一如既往地好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 手滑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員戰鬥準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各班進入迎擊狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆裂吧 現實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綻開吧 神經突觸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vanishment this world！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漆黑物質烈焰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Dark Matter Blaze
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然如此輕鬆地彈開了主人的漆黑物質烈焰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(614,438)\fs21}Dark Matter Blaze
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然如此之強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊中 然後粉碎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L·O·V·E
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就用物理攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Direct Impact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔神鑒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Machine Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑翼護盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,438)\fs21}Schwarz Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arro stire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.72,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs21}注：アロスティーレ，意大利语，烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arro stire是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是烤箱燒烤的意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同居…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.05,0:18:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏不對了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在交往的兩人同住在一個屋檐之下對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想像些什麼下流的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說下流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說著的你其實才是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就沒有想像那些東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.07,0:18:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守我才沒有在想那些不要臉的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉都紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個小鬼卻意外地…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴閉嘴 你這個巨乳傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛的啦 快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同居什麼的不過就是同居而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 真的不是那麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是無可奈何…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:19:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中男生就和已經確定戀愛關係的我的妹妹同居了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說你們之間沒有戀愛關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放棄了盟約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰甩掉了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要咬住不放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那件事我說的是同居那件事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們確實在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是因為讓六花一個人生活我很擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經住了大概一周了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也根本沒有發生那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我回去啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底事實如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約並無特別變化
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以都說了 與其說是同居…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這是合租房屋！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合租房屋 差不多就是那種感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我會接受那種歪理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我會允許嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的書
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 兩個人住是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊給我去找屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意的話 我就把六花帶到意大利去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意大利？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔術結社 紅衣主教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把我帶到那種地方幽禁起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到意大利 那可是超自然的發源地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈感 梵蒂岡 第六感
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然的發源地…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼你看起來好像突然有點想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.46,0:20:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樟葉 你為什麼會出現？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該已經聽說過新學期開始我就會回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說…從誰那裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和六花同學一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為六花同學沒屋子住對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們家也有空房間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話 我也很擔心六花的獨居生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你妹妹監視你我就沒什麼好擔心的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 請讓我繼續在這裏待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就趕緊去找屋子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 和六花的兩人生活很快就宣告了終結
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.53,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嶄新的三人生活於這個春天啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直藉著忘記還了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.07,0:21:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的鄰居搬進來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法取消房屋退約合同也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:22.82,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur2\bord1\3c&HDB00E9&}芽吹いた闇夜が 波乱へと爬行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.94,0:22:25.24,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur2\bord1\3c&H56FF26&}わくわくするねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:29.95,ED1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur2\bord1\3c&HDB00E9&}七つの音 永劫より放たれて
